title: Projected Business Formations Within 4 Quarters for Vermont (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFPBF4QTOTALSAVT (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFPBF4QTOTALSAVT) for an alternative.

The projected number of employer businesses that originate from Business Applications (BA) within four quarters from the quarter of application.
